Liane is a set of open and free technologies and solutions, developed by Instituto Update to boost innovative and low-cost political campaigns in Latin America.

Offers access to powerful tools empowering campaigns that seeks political innovation, that being the development of practices to bring citizens closer to politics, fight inequalities and strengthen democracy.
Mapping of actions in the territory
Need help or would like to report a problem? Write to contato@liane.cc and talk to our team.

Instituto Update is a not-for-profit civil society organization that fosters political innovation in Latin America. Develops intelligence and civic technology projects to bring citizens closer to politics and strengthen democracy based on the vision of political renovation centered on diversity and combating inequalities.
The name is a tribute to Liane Lira, friend and activist who passed away in 2015 and dedicated her life to processes of mobilization, strengthening democracy and political transparency.
